[
  {
    "startTime": 0.15,
    "endTime": 2.473,
    "text": "They can claw through human skin instantly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.653,
    "endTime": 3.485,
    "text": "(shrieks)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 3.486,
    "endTime": 5.2,
    "text": "Pocahontas, this one's for you girl."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.373,
    "endTime": 8.123000000000001,
    "text": "(dramatic music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 10.36,
    "endTime": 11.652,
    "text": "Hey Selorm?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.7,
    "endTime": 12.533,
    "text": "Yeah?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 12.533,
    "endTime": 13.809,
    "text": "You know who has really tiny hands?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.81,
    "endTime": 15.530000000000001,
    "text": "My girl scout leader."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 15.14,
    "endTime": 17.17,
    "text": "No, raccoons."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 17.17,
    "endTime": 18.630000000000003,
    "text": "There's a scene in Pocahontas,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.63,
    "endTime": 20.22,
    "text": "it's like a beautiful setting,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.22,
    "endTime": 22.279,
    "text": "and her hair's gettin all breezy 'cause it's like colors"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.28,
    "endTime": 23.28,
    "text": "of the wind (animal squeaking) happening."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 23.28,
    "endTime": 25.84,
    "text": "So she's like, oh my god I have so much"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.84,
    "endTime": 27.233,
    "text": "like beautiful long hair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 27.24,
    "endTime": 28.84,
    "text": "Who am I gonna turn to to braid my hair?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 28.84,
    "endTime": 31.873,
    "text": "Do I have any friends in the woodlands area?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.88,
    "endTime": 32.713,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.713,
    "endTime": 34.160000000000004,
    "text": "- She has one friend actually. - Who?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.16,
    "endTime": 35.239,
    "text": "[Selorm] That girl with the ponytail."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 35.24,
    "endTime": 37.293,
    "text": "Okay well, John Smith sucks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.36,
    "endTime": 39.7,
    "text": "I need a creature friend that has a thumb."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.7,
    "endTime": 42.7,
    "text": "It's Meeko, a raccoon, her BFF."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 42.7,
    "endTime": 43.220000000000006,
    "text": "No rubber band needed."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.22,
    "endTime": 45.98,
    "text": "No hairspray, this was like bllddadeep done."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.98,
    "endTime": 47.18,
    "text": "Then she's just like on her way."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 47.18,
    "endTime": 49.42,
    "text": "It's like straight off of Instagram beautiful"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.42,
    "endTime": 52.99,
    "text": "and I need to know, if a raccoon can do that for me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.99,
    "endTime": 54.800000000000004,
    "text": "I don't like raccoons, I have to be real with you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 54.8,
    "endTime": 55.632,
    "text": "Why?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.633,
    "endTime": 57.71,
    "text": "You want a little raccoon that's been"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.71,
    "endTime": 59.89,
    "text": "digging through the trash, sharp teeth, rabies,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 59.89,
    "endTime": 61.19,
    "text": "digging through your hair?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 61.84,
    "endTime": 62.673,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.673,
    "endTime": 64.75,
    "text": "First of all, raccoons are (horn squeaking) cute,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 64.75,
    "endTime": 66.12,
    "text": "and I wanna hang out with one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 66.12,
    "endTime": 68.9,
    "text": "And second of all, I wanna see if this is true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.9,
    "endTime": 69.92,
    "text": "The only way we're gonna know for sure is"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 69.92,
    "endTime": 71.48,
    "text": "if you try it out so, let's do it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.48,
    "endTime": 73.13000000000001,
    "text": "Little hands, they're so small."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 73.235,
    "endTime": 75.985,
    "text": "(bones clacking)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 76.67,
    "endTime": 78.899,
    "text": "(whimsical music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 82.206,
    "endTime": 84.39,
    "text": "Oh my god who are you?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 84.91,
    "endTime": 86.179,
    "text": "Hi I'm Crystal."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.18,
    "endTime": 88.30000000000001,
    "text": "I train all kinds of different animals"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 88.3,
    "endTime": 89.5,
    "text": "for the movie industry."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 89.5,
    "endTime": 89.883,
    "text": "[Both] Wow!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.68,
    "endTime": 93.18,
    "text": "I've been told that you can't just walk up to a raccoon"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 93.18,
    "endTime": 94.80300000000001,
    "text": "and go like hey braid my hair. (animal squeaking)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 94.803,
    "endTime": 96.149,
    "text": "They are way more intelligent"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 96.15,
    "endTime": 97.89,
    "text": "than most people give them credit for."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 97.89,
    "endTime": 101.53,
    "text": "They're kind of like a cross between a cat and a monkey."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.53,
    "endTime": 102.363,
    "text": "They're very mischievous."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.363,
    "endTime": 104.29,
    "text": "They can be very aggressive when they want to be."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 104.29,
    "endTime": 105.7,
    "text": "When do they wanna be aggressive?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.7,
    "endTime": 107.15,
    "text": "[Crystal] When they want their stuff"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 107.15,
    "endTime": 108.18,
    "text": "and you don't give it to them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 108.18,
    "endTime": 109.63000000000001,
    "text": "What are the dangers involved"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.63,
    "endTime": 110.92,
    "text": "with a raccoon braiding your hair?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 110.92,
    "endTime": 111.753,
    "text": "[Crystal] If they wanted to,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.753,
    "endTime": 113.58,
    "text": "they could do some serious damage."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 113.58,
    "endTime": 115.49,
    "text": "You have an animal with really sharp teeth,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.49,
    "endTime": 116.36,
    "text": "and really sharp claws."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 116.36,
    "endTime": 117.193,
    "text": "Like how sharp?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 117.193,
    "endTime": 120.567,
    "text": "Between a house cat and a lion."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.567,
    "endTime": 121.72,
    "text": "(roaring) (gasping)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.72,
    "endTime": 122.62,
    "text": "- Do they have rabies?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 122.62,
    "endTime": 124.173,
    "text": "- They can carry rabies, yes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.343,
    "endTime": 125.176,
    "text": "- Oh."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 125.176,
    "endTime": 126.92,
    "text": "- [Crystal] One of the raccoons is not a big fan of blondes."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 126.92,
    "endTime": 129.633,
    "text": "- Guys our director is blonde, what does it mean?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.0,
    "endTime": 132.75,
    "text": "- [Selorm] Can a raccoon braid her hair like in Pocahontas?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 132.75,
    "endTime": 134.96,
    "text": "- Braids are kinda complicated but maybe,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.96,
    "endTime": 136.71,
    "text": "I'm just that good of an animal trainer,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 136.71,
    "endTime": 139.16,
    "text": "and I'll teach my raccoon how to braid your hair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.3,
    "endTime": 142.57000000000002,
    "text": "- Oh that's what I like to hear, someone confident!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.57,
    "endTime": 142.89,
    "text": "We're gonna go training."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.89,
    "endTime": 144.982,
    "text": "I know that like, death, important."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 145.2,
    "endTime": 147.952,
    "text": "Raccoon accepting me and loving me, more important."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.24,
    "endTime": 152.24,
    "text": "We're here today, training with Hollywood Animals."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.24,
    "endTime": 153.89000000000001,
    "text": "We're about to meet two raccoons."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.1,
    "endTime": 155.942,
    "text": "That are super smart I hope."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 157.27,
    "endTime": 158.17000000000002,
    "text": "- [Crystal] Daisy!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 158.388,
    "endTime": 159.221,
    "text": "(chewing)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.221,
    "endTime": 160.72,
    "text": "The raccoon will have to be on a leash."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.72,
    "endTime": 162.93,
    "text": "If anything were to happen, we can pull them off."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.93,
    "endTime": 165.34300000000002,
    "text": "- At first I'm gonna kinda face away,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 165.41,
    "endTime": 168.22,
    "text": "not really make eye contact, because that can be"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 168.22,
    "endTime": 170.4,
    "text": "a little bit intimidating and stressful for them."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.4,
    "endTime": 172.20000000000002,
    "text": "I love raccoons and I hope they love me"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.2,
    "endTime": 173.29899999999998,
    "text": "or I'll be devastated."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 173.3,
    "endTime": 175.453,
    "text": "Highlight of my life, lil' tiny hands."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 177.21,
    "endTime": 178.43,
    "text": "Here we go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.454,
    "endTime": 181.204,
    "text": "(dramatic music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 185.19,
    "endTime": 186.755,
    "text": "(chewing)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.755,
    "endTime": 189.505,
    "text": "(dramatic music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 191.19,
    "endTime": 193.29,
    "text": "- We hit the clicker and feed them,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 193.29,
    "endTime": 195.92,
    "text": "so they understand that every time we click,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.92,
    "endTime": 197.792,
    "text": "they get paid with food."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 199.4,
    "endTime": 201.69,
    "text": "- I'm really shocked that in the first time meeting them,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.69,
    "endTime": 205.0,
    "text": "they were immediately doing pretty close to what"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.0,
    "endTime": 206.453,
    "text": "it looks like in Pocahontas."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.453,
    "endTime": 207.703,
    "text": "- [Crystal] Take it over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 207.76,
    "endTime": 208.593,
    "text": "Can you take it over?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.593,
    "endTime": 210.993,
    "text": "- Can they actually braid?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.11,
    "endTime": 211.943,
    "text": "I don't know."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 211.943,
    "endTime": 214.31,
    "text": "They are talented, smart, beautiful creatures."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 214.31,
    "endTime": 216.9,
    "text": "I can't hug them, which is fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.9,
    "endTime": 217.44,
    "text": "Kind of like they're a celeb."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.44,
    "endTime": 219.67,
    "text": "But Selorm's gonna lose her mind when she sees"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 219.67,
    "endTime": 221.63,
    "text": "these raccoons because they're so cute."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.63,
    "endTime": 223.19,
    "text": "No, actually she hates them, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 223.19,
    "endTime": 224.683,
    "text": "This is the best day of my life."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.683,
    "endTime": 227.183,
    "text": "(happy music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.153,
    "endTime": 232.903,
    "text": "Ooh, they're so cute!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.4,
    "endTime": 236.23000000000002,
    "text": "The paws feel like little tiny baby hands."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 236.24,
    "endTime": 239.59300000000002,
    "text": "They're beautiful, very smart, very smart."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.65,
    "endTime": 241.23000000000002,
    "text": "Oh you wanna play?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.232,
    "endTime": 243.65,
    "text": "(giggles)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 243.18,
    "endTime": 244.133,
    "text": "I love you so much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.833,
    "endTime": 245.666,
    "text": "(giggles)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.666,
    "endTime": 248.14,
    "text": "I get it Pocahontas, this is the (animal squeaking)."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.633,
    "endTime": 250.70000000000002,
    "text": "(happy music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.7,
    "endTime": 252.10899999999998,
    "text": "Today is the day, my friends."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.11,
    "endTime": 255.99,
    "text": "We've got drama, we've got danger, we've got Disney."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 255.99,
    "endTime": 257.329,
    "text": "You know what else we have?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 257.329,
    "endTime": 258.163,
    "text": "- Doritos."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.163,
    "endTime": 258.99600000000004,
    "text": "- Tiny little hands."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 258.995,
    "endTime": 262.49,
    "text": "I spent the entire day training with two raccoons."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.5,
    "endTime": 263.174,
    "text": "Sometimes they feel like doing"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.174,
    "endTime": 264.21,
    "text": "(animal squeaking) sometimes they don't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 264.21,
    "endTime": 266.15,
    "text": "Which honestly, is like all of us, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.15,
    "endTime": 267.179,
    "text": "We just lay it out for you,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 267.18,
    "endTime": 269.43,
    "text": "all the stuff that you have to do if you wanna like,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.43,
    "endTime": 271.51,
    "text": "chill with a raccoon, which you shouldn't do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.51,
    "endTime": 273.9,
    "text": "First off, never poach a raccoon in the wild."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.9,
    "endTime": 274.95,
    "text": "They could have rabies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 274.95,
    "endTime": 276.59999999999997,
    "text": "- They probably have rabies."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.6,
    "endTime": 276.89300000000003,
    "text": "- That's not true."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.893,
    "endTime": 279.11899999999997,
    "text": "They don't probably have it, they might have it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.39,
    "endTime": 280.223,
    "text": "- She's getting rabies today."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 280.223,
    "endTime": 281.56,
    "text": "- Calm down."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.56,
    "endTime": 283.0,
    "text": "They have really sharp (animal squeaking) teeth."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.0,
    "endTime": 284.17,
    "text": "Don't make eye contact,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 284.17,
    "endTime": 285.42,
    "text": "and I am not (animal squeaking) around."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 285.42,
    "endTime": 286.53000000000003,
    "text": "Don't make eye contact."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.53,
    "endTime": 287.9,
    "text": "They have sharp (animal squeaking) claws."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.9,
    "endTime": 290.39,
    "text": "They might be all like pitter pattering around,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.4,
    "endTime": 291.23999999999995,
    "text": "like eating lil snackies,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.24,
    "endTime": 293.33,
    "text": "but those things are really sharp and they can literally"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 293.33,
    "endTime": 295.19,
    "text": "claw through human skin instantly."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.19,
    "endTime": 298.653,
    "text": "If you have any food near you, just like, don't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.128,
    "endTime": 299.961,
    "text": "- Don't do it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 299.961,
    "endTime": 300.79400000000004,
    "text": "- Just like don't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.794,
    "endTime": 301.627,
    "text": "They're like."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.66,
    "endTime": 302.49300000000005,
    "text": "(slapping and screaming)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.493,
    "endTime": 304.8,
    "text": "I'm willing to take this chance for all the Disney fans,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.8,
    "endTime": 307.47,
    "text": "the nay sayers, the raccoon haters."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 307.47,
    "endTime": 308.30300000000005,
    "text": "- Damn."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.303,
    "endTime": 309.136,
    "text": "- How are you feeling based on"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 309.136,
    "endTime": 310.55,
    "text": "my one day of raccoon training."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.55,
    "endTime": 312.15000000000003,
    "text": "- Do you know they had us all sign waivers today?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 312.15,
    "endTime": 313.82,
    "text": "Even our sound person signed a waiver."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 313.82,
    "endTime": 316.32,
    "text": "There's no going back now, you gotta do the thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 316.88,
    "endTime": 317.77,
    "text": "I wish you the best."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 317.77,
    "endTime": 320.18,
    "text": "- Pocahontas, this one's for you girl."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 320.18,
    "endTime": 321.13,
    "text": "Let's go."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 321.94,
    "endTime": 323.88,
    "text": "I'm here in my fake (animal squeaking) forest."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 323.88,
    "endTime": 325.293,
    "text": "Selorm how are you feeling?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 325.7,
    "endTime": 327.603,
    "text": "- I'm fine, I'm fine."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.66,
    "endTime": 328.49300000000005,
    "text": "- You scared?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.493,
    "endTime": 329.326,
    "text": "- No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 329.326,
    "endTime": 330.15900000000005,
    "text": "- You nervous?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 330.159,
    "endTime": 330.992,
    "text": "- No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.57,
    "endTime": 332.55,
    "text": "- That looks like a lie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 332.55,
    "endTime": 334.503,
    "text": "- Mm mm. (laughs)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 335.9,
    "endTime": 339.7,
    "text": "- I need to put my hair into three beautiful strands"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 339.7,
    "endTime": 341.56,
    "text": "for the raccoon to grab just like"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 341.56,
    "endTime": 343.15,
    "text": "you would if you were doing a braid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 343.15,
    "endTime": 343.983,
    "text": "- Very trendy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 343.983,
    "endTime": 345.823,
    "text": "- Thank you so much."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 345.93,
    "endTime": 348.19,
    "text": "I'm using tiny little rubber bands because their"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 348.19,
    "endTime": 351.19,
    "text": "teeny little hands need a teeny little rubber band to match."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 351.2,
    "endTime": 352.729,
    "text": "- You're so creepy with this tiny hands thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 352.73,
    "endTime": 354.51300000000003,
    "text": "- It's not creepy, it's just love."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.69,
    "endTime": 356.79,
    "text": "Bring in the raccoons."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 357.391,
    "endTime": 360.641,
    "text": "(tense dramatic music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 362.781,
    "endTime": 365.11400000000003,
    "text": "(crunching)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 371.313,
    "endTime": 373.229,
    "text": "- [Crystal] Pick it up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 381.2,
    "endTime": 383.163,
    "text": "- Alright dudes, so far so good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 383.301,
    "endTime": 384.134,
    "text": "- Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 384.134,
    "endTime": 387.18,
    "text": "- I'm very hopeful, very inspired."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 387.18,
    "endTime": 391.11,
    "text": "- This is not church, can we just do this thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 392.813,
    "endTime": 394.163,
    "text": "- This is it baby."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 395.15,
    "endTime": 396.2,
    "text": "- I really hope this works."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 396.2,
    "endTime": 397.522,
    "text": "- [Crystal] Daisy, get up there!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 398.352,
    "endTime": 399.185,
    "text": "(clicking)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 399.185,
    "endTime": 400.18,
    "text": "Good, pick it up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 401.61,
    "endTime": 402.44300000000004,
    "text": "Put it here."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 404.49,
    "endTime": 405.32300000000004,
    "text": "Good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 405.7,
    "endTime": 407.33,
    "text": "- Ooh, it's a tight grab."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 409.23,
    "endTime": 411.18,
    "text": "Daisy's getting it, she's almost there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 419.54,
    "endTime": 420.19800000000004,
    "text": "(record scratching)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 420.198,
    "endTime": 422.864,
    "text": "(playful music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 427.4,
    "endTime": 430.513,
    "text": "- Daisy attempted a (animal squeaking) braid."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 431.22,
    "endTime": 433.63000000000005,
    "text": "But, she was like, I'm gonna start a braid, I'm done."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 434.156,
    "endTime": 435.17,
    "text": "I'm just gonna do it, that's it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 435.17,
    "endTime": 436.38,
    "text": "I need a moment of mourning."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 436.38,
    "endTime": 438.46,
    "text": "I thought this would happen, and it didn't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 438.46,
    "endTime": 439.293,
    "text": "- Okay."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 440.576,
    "endTime": 441.40900000000005,
    "text": "(shimmering)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 441.409,
    "endTime": 442.242,
    "text": "- Not to be biased,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 442.242,
    "endTime": 444.67,
    "text": "but I think this is one of my favorite experiments."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 444.67,
    "endTime": 446.923,
    "text": "But, I have some sad news to report."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 446.94,
    "endTime": 447.853,
    "text": "This...."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 447.929,
    "endTime": 449.659,
    "text": "(sad music)"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 449.66,
    "endTime": 450.793,
    "text": "was bogus."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 451.26,
    "endTime": 452.349,
    "text": "Raccoons can't braid hair."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 452.35,
    "endTime": 454.42,
    "text": "That's like (animal squeaking) that that's how life is,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 454.42,
    "endTime": 457.41,
    "text": "but a braid involves crossing, weaving,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 457.41,
    "endTime": 459.47,
    "text": "all into one beautiful strand."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 459.47,
    "endTime": 460.483,
    "text": "And raccoons."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 460.74,
    "endTime": 461.57300000000004,
    "text": "- Couldn't do it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 461.573,
    "endTime": 463.12,
    "text": "- Pocahontas, this one's for you girl."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 463.23,
    "endTime": 464.233,
    "text": "We did it for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 464.89,
    "endTime": 466.233,
    "text": "Even though it's fake."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 466.783,
    "endTime": 468.95,
    "text": "(humming)"
  }
]